agraph3">Hey everyone! It’s Jaden, and today, I will tell you all about my first day of senior school. It was a busy and exciting day, so let’s dive right in!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7704" data-pf-type="Section" id="text_image" class="sc-dxcExB gjNMyZ pf-30_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-kqGpvY OSjcf"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-31_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:5px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-32_"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-33_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-34_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Starting_Senior_School_Tips_How_to_Tackle_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746040" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Starting_Senior_School_Tips_How_to_Tackle_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746040 1536w" width="2240" height="1493" alt="Starting Senior School Tips How to Tackle Your First Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Starting Senior School Tips How to Tackle Your First Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-35_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-36_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Wavebreakmedia via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-38_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-39_ pf-heading-1-h3">Using my locker for the first time</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-41_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">One of the best parts about senior school is that I finally get to use a locker! I have a key for it, and there's something satisfying about opening and closing it. Plus, I have a card to access different school buildings, which makes me feel quite grown-up</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-43_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-44_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-45_ pf-heading-1-h3">My first lessons</h3><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-47_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">On my first day, I had several lessons: Physics, Geography, Maths, and RE (Religious Education). Physics was fun because we talked about units of measurement like mass and weight. I wasn’t sure about Geography at first, but my new teacher made it fun, so I think I’ll enjoy it this year.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-49_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/First_Day_School_Experiences_Lockers_Lessons_and_New_Friends_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746210" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/First_Day_School_Experiences_Lockers_Lessons_and_New_Friends_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746210 1536w" width="2645" height="1764" alt="First Day School Experiences Lockers, Lessons, and New Friends - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="First Day School Experiences Lockers, Lessons, and New Friends - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-50_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-51_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-53_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;