out five minutes, so I was a little late, but now I know my way around the school. I’ve figured out where the Physics room, Maths room, and even the Modern Languages rooms are.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-69_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746421" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746421 1536w" width="2688" height="1793" alt="Navigating Senior School Tips for Finding Your Way on Day One - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Navigating Senior School Tips for Finding Your Way on Day One - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-70_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-71_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Wavebreakmedia via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-73_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-74_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746537" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746537 1536w" width="1920" height="1280" alt="Using Lockers in School Why It’s One of the Coolest Parts of Senior School - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Using Lockers in School Why It’s One of the Coolest Parts of Senior School - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type=