/Senior_School_Orientation_Day_What_to_Expect_on_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746318 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Senior_School_Orientation_Day_What_to_Expect_on_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1726746318 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Senior_School_Orientation_Day_What_to_Expect_on_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1726746318 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Senior_School_Orientation_Day_What_to_Expect_on_Your_First_Day_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1726746318 320w" width="1664" height="1109" alt="Senior School Orientation Day What to Expect on Your First Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Senior School Orientation Day What to Expect on Your First Day - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-108_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-109_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by monkeybusiness via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-111_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">I also got to meet some new kids. One of them is named Ben, and even though we’re not friends yet, we had a good chat, especially since we ended up sitting next to each other in Physics. I also sat near some of my old friends, like Josh and Tyler, so having a mix of familiar faces and new people was nice.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-113_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-114_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-115_ pf-heading-1-h3">Getting lost</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746421" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746421 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1726746421 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1726746421 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Navigating_Senior_School_Tips_for_Finding_Your_Way_on_Day_One_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1726746421 320w" width="2688" height="1793" alt="Navigating Senior School Tips for Finding Your Way on Day One - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Navigating Senior School Tips for Finding Your Way on Day One - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-117_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-118_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Wavebreakmedia via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-120_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">One of the funniest parts of my day was when I got lost trying to find my classroom! It cost me about five minutes, so I was a little late, but now I know my way around the school. I’ve figured out where the Physics room, Maths room, and even the Modern Languages rooms are.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-122_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-md:5px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-123_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-124_ pf-heading-1-h3">School food - A new treat!</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746537" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1726746537 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.jpg?v=1726746537 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1726746537 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Using_Lockers_in_School_Why_It_s_One_of_the_Coolest_Parts_of_Senior_School_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1726746537 320w" width="1920" height="1280" alt="Using Lockers in School Why It’s One of the Coolest Parts of Senior School - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Using Lockers in School Why It’s One of the Coolest Parts of Senior School - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gdyfxU iluFjz pf-126_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-127_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Pressmaster via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iMWBWc laPXAE pf-129_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">For lunch, I had some pasta, half of my sandwich, a cookie, and some soda. I’m really excited about the school food—apparently, they even have chicken wings sometimes! I’ll be looking forward to lunch in the coming days.<br><br>Overall, my first day was great. I’m still getting used to the size of the school, but I had a lot of fun and learned a lot. Senior school will be a good adventure, and I can’t wait to see what happens next.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-ca02" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dxcExB gjNMyZ pf-131_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-kqGpvY OSjcf"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-132_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:5px;--s